Are you a part of this company?

35:24.706 --> 35:30.435
If you're at part, you can smile and say, thank you, Lord.

35:30.455 --> 35:32.197
Thank you for I found this church.

35:35.001 --> 35:42.653
Thank you for leading me to be a member of this great company, the Church of God.

35:47.120 --> 35:48.722
Have you had that experience?

35:51.394 --> 35:55.319
Did you accept him as your savior at a certain time in your life?

35:56.820 --> 35:57.942
If you answer me, yes.

36:00.144 --> 36:02.027
Shout, stop to finish.

36:02.047 --> 36:06.352
Shout afterwards, don't shout now.

36:06.372 --> 36:08.594
Enjoy your life in Christ.

36:09.896 --> 36:15.122
You'll secure now, tomorrow, and the future.

36:21.730 --> 36:28.558
This old company takes care of your needs.

36:30.760 --> 36:33.944
If someone is sick, we pray for them.

36:34.745 --> 36:36.527
Did God answered our prayers?

36:38.369 --> 36:39.130
Yes or no?

36:40.291 --> 36:40.711
Amen.

36:40.852 --> 36:43.615
Thank you.

36:43.635 --> 36:50.162
If someone we know a family is indeed that church,

36:51.586 --> 36:53.027
runs to help.

36:56.711 --> 36:59.314
This is the oldest company.

36:59.854 --> 37:02.797
Still the rules and regulations, the same.

37:03.197 --> 37:05.460
They did not change with time.

37:06.180 --> 37:08.863
They did not change with centuries.

37:09.163 --> 37:10.264
They did not change.

37:10.645 --> 37:11.726
It will not change.

37:12.546 --> 37:13.527
It will not change.

37:13.848 --> 37:14.869
Love is the same.

37:15.670 --> 37:16.991
Salvation is the same.

37:17.631 --> 37:18.753
Living is the same.

37:19.894 --> 37:20.274
And

37:20.354 --> 37:21.456
We know very well.

37:22.217 --> 37:33.353
He who started this, the Lord Jesus Christ on that day, on that day, and the Holy Spirit started winning souls for us.

37:33.874 --> 37:37.560
Did not change because he says, I am God.

37:38.341 --> 37:39.222
I do not change.

37:46.153 --> 37:49.778
So why do I go to church?

37:51.586 --> 37:53.167
Ask yourself this question.

37:54.749 --> 37:56.531
Ask yourself.

37:56.551 --> 37:59.593
I give you two, three points there.

38:00.594 --> 38:21.554
And let us pray that we will always look forward to come to church, to honor God, and to live according to what we hear according to what we are taught and go out.

38:22.434 --> 38:26.037
and be a good witness to the whole world.

38:27.098 --> 38:27.439
Amen.

38:28.480 --> 38:30.862
Let's buy our heads for prayers.

38:33.144 --> 38:45.836
Thank you, Father, for allowing us to meditate a little bit on why coming to church and how can we affect it in our lives.

38:47.158 --> 38:48.579
Bless each and everyone.

38:49.720 --> 38:51.762
May you be with each and every family.

38:52.642 --> 38:58.210
and help us Lord, to be true witnesses to what happened.

38:58.231 --> 39:13.514
And to be proud, when we are asked about our life, to be proud, to tell them that I belong to the oldest company in the world, the Church of Jesus Christ.

39:14.315 --> 39:17.300
Dismiss us, we pray, in Jesus name, amen.

39:17.900 --> 39:19.042
The meeting is over.

39:19.062 --> 39:20.124
Thank you for listening.

39:20.925 --> 39:21.586
God bless you.

